Package gg.sep.alyx.plugins

Class PluginManagerPlugin

  • java.lang.Object
    • gg.sep.alyx.plugin.AlyxPlugin<NoOpPluginData>
      • gg.sep.alyx.plugin.StatelessAlyxPlugin
        • gg.sep.alyx.plugins.PluginManagerPlugin
  • public class PluginManagerPlugin
extends StatelessAlyxPlugin
    Default plugin for managing other plugins in Alyx. This plugin is guarded, and cannot be unloaded without an explicit override. See AlyxPlugin.isGuarded() for info.
